{"tid":1952134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柬埔寨限制部分食米出口　本港米商：不影響供應","createTime":"2020-03-31T12:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T13:39:58.000Z","uid":124526,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8df5cd7cbcca21055be804d697768e4b9574dd73","tid":1952134,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200331/mobile/bkn-20200331124408084-0331_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200331%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200331124408084-0331_00822_001.html&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=796e749a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200331/mobile/bkn-20200331124408084-0331_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"eb0ba2fcfcae0584a9ccf5eded381ac4ec37b37d","tid":1952134,"uid":124526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情令全球各地爆搶糧潮，柬埔寨宣布4月5日起禁止白米和糙米出口，香米則未受影響。香港米行商會理事長陳建年指，進口本港的柬埔寨米佔全港米量不足10%，加上當中90%進口香港的柬埔寨米屬香米，認為本港食米供應不會受該措施影響，呼籲市民毋須擔心。<br />\n<br />\n陳建年指出，柬埔寨的食米分為白米、糙米及香米，本港進口以香米為主，因較高級及優質，目前當地的措施不會影響本港的食米供應。他又指，現時屬業界的「季尾」，米商會陸續補貨，應付下一季供應，相信現時各商戶有多於1個月的食米存量，重申港人毋須憂慮供應。<br />\n<br />\n工業貿易署資料顯示，截至2月29日，本港進口食米中，泰國米佔最多，達2.83萬公噸，佔整體53.1%；其次是越南米，達1.36萬公噸，佔整體25.5%。來自柬埔寨的食米進口約5千公噸，佔整體9.4%。消費者委員會早前表示，已與香港食品委員會聯絡，該會確認香港的食米供應穩定，呼籲市民毋須恐慌搶購。"},{"pid":"94407669d23daa56f97d58aa83098810f505b87b","tid":1952134,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"重要Post，唔該幫推啊！！<br />\n<br />\n【告急】呢一刻最逼切亦最有用嘅聯署<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fktGmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fktGmS</a>"},{"pid":"11f9eee35a922fc79a94a14f0c0ae9484534d5a1","tid":1952134,"uid":180204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"搶定米先"},{"pid":"971cd72ce51c4a75a2cdc1834e3b36328b54edd8","tid":1952134,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f9eee35a922fc79a94a14f0c0ae9484534d5a1","tid":1952134,"uid":180204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:17:30.000Z","msg":"搶定米先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"使唔使啊？"},{"pid":"7fa7a9a793d42a49021fcb41e5d0069ae969bafc","tid":1952134,"uid":15605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"驚閪，最多食餸唔食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e590e27ee9ad0a4c128dbadc2fd6e9dac93bb1","tid":1952134,"uid":112622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:28:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a412e1723bc40c2c93b3005468658f005ee7bc3","tid":1952134,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"泰國一封埋就玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9b8ebd3fa0474058479a809e8a8de8a3ee8188","tid":1952134,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T12:40:27.000Z","msg":"泰國今年旱災，不過出口點都有。只係可能少過上年。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.udnbkk.com/article-296088-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.udnbkk.com%2Farticle-296088-1.html&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhnljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=f17bac23\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.udnbkk.com/article-296088-1.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb2f66e055347987685bcd65e58c0b6c76c33890","tid":1952134,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"日本米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bfabd097d34dd6b04de96b2a484c6402318d87","tid":1952134,"uid":124526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T13:39:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1952291\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1952291</a>"}]}